ReutersMessageFormat.name: MarketByPrice
ReutersMessageFormat.Description: MarketByPrice provides access to market depth information, Market depth information is level II data that is aggregrated by price and data.

field.name: MARKET STAT
field.description: Indicates the current futures market status including whether a fast market condition exists.

field.name: EXCHANGE ID 2
field.description: Identifier for the exchange on which the instrument trades. This field is a two-byte replacement for FID4 RDN_EXCHID and contains a super-set of this field's range of values.

field.name: CURRENCY
field.description: The currency in which the instrument is quoted.

field.name: TRADING UNITS
field.description: The price units in which the issue trades.

field.name: Action
field.description: Action used to add/delete/update an entry's contents. UPDATE 1 Action used to update an entry's contents. If this entry does not exist in cache, it should be ignored and thrown out. If the entitlement check on the permission data fails, then the data should be ignored and thrown out. ADD 2 Action used to add or replace an entire entry. If this action is received in an update message for an entry that has not been received in a refresh, this entry can optionally be ignored because the entry will be received again in a subsequent refresh message. If the entitlement check on the permission data fails, then the action should be changed to DELETE_ACTION, and the permission data and entry data should be removed from the entry. ADD_ACTION operations can be conflated on a per entry basis by ignoring the previous action and on-passing the most recent ADD_ACTION. DELETE 3 Action used to remove an entry. The data at the key of this entry should be removed. If the entry does not exist in a cache, then the entry should be ignored and thrown out. Data is never provided for this entry.

field.name: BID
field.description: Latest bid price.For US Composite stock and equity market maker super records the best bid price. For OM type option markets the block bid price.

field.name: ASK
field.description: Latest ask price.For US Composite stock and equity market maker super records the best ask price. For OM type option markets the block ask price.

field.name: ASK SIZE
field.description: The quantity offered at the latest ask price - in the case of equity market maker super records the total quantity offered at the best ask price. For Australian futures the number of selling contracts.

field.name: BID SIZE
field.description: The quantity bid at the latest bid price - in the case of equity market maker super records the total quantity bid at the best bid price. For Australian futures the number of buying contracts.
